rows.label: tev046001_SEL2021
rows.name: Ask Lavina about recent developments.

rows.label: tev046001_MSG0001
rows.name:
For short and stubby race, you are strong.
Also wise and honest.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev046001_MSG0002
rows.name: Earth aliens also saved us from Ganglion![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev046001_MSG0003
rows.name:
Some Prone may turn up noses at your strange
mechanical bodies.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev046001_MSG0004
rows.name: But I know your bodies still have passionate souls.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev046001_MSG0005
rows.name: Count on Prone to help any way we can![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev046001_MSG0008
rows.name: I am in love, Earth alien. This man has won my heart![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev046001_MSG0009
rows.name:
When I met Leroy on beach,
I knew he must be my mate.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev046001_MSG0010
rows.name: Never have I felt so about Prone males. It is strange.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev046001_MSG0011
rows.name:
But I worry what Father will say.
His way of thinking is old way.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev046001_MSG0012
rows.name:
Still, love has sunk fangs into me and I must obey.
Do Earth aliens know this feeling?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev046001_MSG0025
rows.name:
I grew up as Ganglion captive.
I know little of homeworld my father speaks of.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev046001_MSG0026
rows.name:
But I still want to learn our traditions.
I want to be ready for day we return home.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev046001_MSG0027
rows.name:
Some Prone say we should let go of old ways.
Say we no longer need them in Earth-alien city.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev046001_MSG0028
rows.name: But what we let go, we never get back. So I hold on.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev046001_MSG0013
rows.name:
You freed me from commitment to Wazdo,
Earth alien! You let me marry man I love![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev046001_MSG0014
rows.name: Father likes Leroy. Even if he will not admit it.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev046001_MSG0015
rows.name: It could not have turned out better![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev046001_MSG0016
rows.name:
I love Leroy. I also love Father.
It is good I did not have to choose.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev046001_MSG0017
rows.name: I have put thought into situation with Leroy and Father.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev046001_MSG0018
rows.name: I was ready to marry Leroy without permission...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev046001_MSG0019
rows.name:
But we will not be happy family unless Father accepts
us. And I want happy family.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev046001_MSG0020
rows.name:
Father has given me and Leroy fair chance.
I know Leroy will not waste it.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev046001_MSG0021
rows.name:
So I will wait as long as it takes.
Things will turn out for best.[ST:wait ]
